
extends baseEmail

block content
  h1 Password Reset Request
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p You requested a password reset for your Fifthlab account.
  p Click the button below to reset your password (link valid for 10 minutes):
  p
    a.btn(href= url) Reset Password
  p If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link:
  a(href= url)= url
  p If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email.